Requirements
------------

* busybox, statically compiled, for the busybox chroot
* cgcreate/cgdelete tools
* a cgroup lurch given to the user:
    cgcreate -a $user -t $user -g cpuacct,memory:lurch
* dockerd running on the host with ideally no other VMs (users will have
  access to them) for the docker containment strategy
* an HTTP server able to run CGI scripts (recommended: lighttpd)

